    <summary><span data-ttu-id="848a2-101">当进入锁定状态的递归与此锁定的递归策略不兼容时引发的异常。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="848a2-101">The exception that is thrown when recursive entry into a lock is not compatible with the recursion policy for the lock.</span></span></summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="848a2-102"><xref:System.Threading.LockRecursionException> 出于以下几个原因引发：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="848a2-102"><xref:System.Threading.LockRecursionException> is thrown for several reasons, including the following:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="848a2-103">如果线程尝试进入递归的实例 <xref:System.Threading.ReaderWriterLockSlim> ，但该实例不支持递归。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="848a2-103">If a thread tries to enter an instance of <xref:System.Threading.ReaderWriterLockSlim> recursively, but the instance does not support recursion.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="848a2-104"><xref:System.Threading.ReaderWriterLockSlim>当线程最初进入读取模式锁定状态时，如果线程尝试进入写入模式或可升级模式下的实例，则为。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="848a2-104">If a thread tries to enter a <xref:System.Threading.ReaderWriterLockSlim> instance in write mode or upgradeable mode when the thread initially entered the lock in read mode.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="848a2-105">这表示潜在的死锁，因此不允许这样做。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="848a2-105">This represents a potential deadlock and therefore is not allowed.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="848a2-106">如果允许一个更高的递归级别超过用于跟踪递归的内部存储计数器的最大值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="848a2-106">If allowing one more level of recursion would exceed the maximum value for the internal storage counter used to track recursions.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="848a2-107">此限制数值很大，因此任何情况下应用程序都不应遇到此情况。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="848a2-107">This limit is so large that applications should never encounter it.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="848a2-108">下面的示例演示使用类的两个原因 <xref:System.Threading.LockRecursionException> <xref:System.Threading.ReaderWriterLockSlim> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="848a2-108">The following example shows two causes of <xref:System.Threading.LockRecursionException> when using the <xref:System.Threading.ReaderWriterLockSlim> class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="848a2-109">程序 <xref:System.Threading.ReaderWriterLockSlim> 使用无参数构造函数创建，该构造函数不允许使用递归。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="848a2-109">The program creates a <xref:System.Threading.ReaderWriterLockSlim> by using the parameterless constructor, which disallows recursion.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="848a2-110">然后，程序将启动进入读取模式锁定状态的线程。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="848a2-110">The program then starts a thread that enters the lock in read mode.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="848a2-111">该线程尝试在读取模式中以递归方式进入锁定状态，并捕获产生的异常。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="848a2-111">The thread tries to enter the lock recursively in read mode, and catches the resulting exception.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="848a2-112">最后，线程尝试进入写入模式，这可能会导致死锁。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="848a2-112">Finally, the thread tries to enter write mode, which would create a potential for deadlocks.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="848a2-113">线程捕获产生的异常。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="848a2-113">The thread catches the resulting exception.</span></span>  
  
